---
// SystemSection.astro — Container 3 (id: 9881de1)
---

<section
  class="relative overflow-hidden
    flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row flex-wrap justify-center items-center
    gap-[20px] xl:gap-0
    px-[5%] pt-[10%] pb-[17%]
    md:px-[5%] md:pt-[10%] md:pb-[10%]
    lg:p-0
    -mt-[30px] md:mt-0
    border-t border-[#FFFFFF0F]"
  style="background-color: #F9F9F9;"
>
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1140px] mx-auto flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-[20px] xl:gap-0 lg:overflow-x-clip lg:overflow-y-visible">

    <!-- Text container (5acd04f) - glassmorphism -->
    <div
      class="w-full lg:w-[44%] p-0 lg:p-[40px]
        bg-transparent lg:bg-[#FFFFFF0D]
        border-0 lg:border lg:border-[#00000024] lg:rounded-[10px]
        z-[99]"
      style="backdrop-filter: blur(20px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);"
    >
      <h2
        class="font-factul font-normal text-[4.4vw] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[32px]
          leading-[1.2em] text-[#1C3124]
          text-center lg:text-left mb-[20px]"
        style="text-wrap: balance;"
      >
        Quando não existe um sistema alimentar claro e estruturado,
        <span class="texto" style="font-weight: 400 !important;">cada refeição exige decisão, adaptação e negociação.</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="font-normal text-[20px] leading-[1.4em] text-[#0F0F0F] text-center lg:text-left"
        style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-weight: 600;">
        <span class="texto">Isso gera desgaste,</span> mesmo em famílias comprometidas.
      </p>

      <p class="font-normal text-[16px] lg:text-[18px] leading-[1.4em] text-[#0F0F0F] text-center lg:text-left mt-[20px]"
        style="font-family: Inter, sans-serif;">
        Famílias que alcançam autonomia alimentar, que veem seus filhos voltarem a comer, não fazem &ldquo;mais força&rdquo;, elas <span class="texto">seguem um processo estruturado, claro, com constância e direção.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Image 1 (d7394c9): mobile full-bleed, hidden desktop -->
    <!-- Original: widget=351px but widget-container=397px (overflow visible, ~102% vw) -->
    <div class="w-[calc(100%+13%)] -mt-[26%] -mr-[7%] -mb-[14%] -ml-[6%] lg:w-0 lg:h-0 lg:overflow-hidden lg:m-0">
      <img
        src="https://comerbemsemestresse.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/115104.webp"
        alt=""
        class="w-full h-auto"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Image 2 (4297d9a): hidden mobile, visible desktop (overflow 905px) -->
    <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-[54%] overflow-visible">
      <div class="lg:w-[905px] lg:max-w-none lg:-ml-[92px]">
        <img
          src="https://comerbemsemestresse.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/091713-copy.webp"
          alt=""
          class="w-full h-auto"
          loading="lazy"
          width="1038"
          height="693"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
